metadata.name: Masivo Silver Corp
metadata.description: Masivo Silver Corp., a junior silver and gold mining company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties. The company holds interests in the El Colomo property covering an area of 18,766 hectares located in Mexico. It also has an option to earn a 100% interest in the Elko Country silver-gold-copper property consisting of 65 unpatented claims covering an area of approximately 543 hectares located in Elko County, Nevada. The company was formerly known as Gainey Capital Corp. and changed its name to Masivo Silver Corp. in March 2021. Masivo Silver Corp. was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
